<h1>1 patay sa 62nd IB sa Canlaon City</h1>
<p>Author: Philippine Revolution Web Central</p>
<p>Publish Time: 2023-02-27T99:00:00-04:00</p>
<p>Modified Time: 2023-02-27T05:40:04+00:00</p>
<p>Description: Patay ang 1 ka katapo sang 62nd IB nga naga-operasyon sa sityo Batang-batangan, Brgy Bucalan, Canlaon City, Negros Oriental alas 5:30 sang hapon sang gin-isnayp sang New People&#039;s Army kahapon Pebrero</p>
